  "Description": {
    "English": "An array of distributed neurons, fused to a board of metallic strands. Complex patterns of electrical impulses weave their way across the surface, knotting each ship system together.<br> <br>Hold <span class=\"name name-img\">THRUST</span> to inquire if the ship would like to take off.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一组分布的神经元，融合在一块金属链上。复杂的电脉冲样式交织在表面上，把每一个舰船系统连接在一起。<br><br>按住<span class=\"name name-img\">THRUST</span>询问船是否要起飞。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "大量神經元經過融合後分布在布滿金屬線的板子上。複雜的電子訊號在表面穿梭，藉此連接太空船的所有系統。<br> <br>按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">THRUST</span> 詢問太空船願不願意起飛。"
  },
